{
  "text": "where\u1e8d d denotes the acceleration response of the differential mode and\u1e8d c denotes the acceleration response of the common mode. To satisfy (3) and (4), the acceleration references of the common mode and the differential mode are described in [CITATION_1] and (7).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "8787884"
